		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="- Load up GustavDev/CTY_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;- Use ReCon command &quot;goto 52 3 -138&quot;&#xD;&#xA;- &quot;killcombat&quot; to kill all the Sahuagin after they appear and attack.&#xD;&#xA;- This dialogue will play after a short delay, between a player who was in that combat and one of the civilians here." />
